        "content": "<div style=\"padding: 4px 2px 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.55;\"><h1 style=\"margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 28px;\">Recent SQLPage traces and logs</h1><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px;\">Open <a href=\"http://localhost\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">http://localhost</a> and interact with the app. New requests will appear here automatically.</p><p style=\"margin: 0; color: #666;\">The trace table shows recent requests. The logs panel shows SQLPage container logs, including the trace ID so you can jump from a log line to the full span waterfall.</p></div>",
        "mode": "html"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.4.0",
      "title": "Overview",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
